column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
I'm sorry, I don't understand the question. Can you please rephrase it?
I am speaking to provide you with medical information and advice.
Are you asking if it is safe to attend school during the Coronavirus pandemic? I recommend following your local health and government guidelines regarding when and how to safely attend school.
